                     <interp inst="t18020918-147-defend979" type="age" value="18"></interp>
                  </persName>
               
             was indicted for <rs id="t18020918-147-off768" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18020918-147-off768" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18020918-147-off768" type="offenceSubcategory" value="theftFromPlace"></interp>
               feloniously stealing, on the <rs id="t18020918-147-cd769" type="crimeDate">7th of August</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18020918-147-off768 t18020918-147-cd769"></join>, a silver watch, value 2l. seven dollars, value 1l. 15s. the property of 
                     <persName id="t18020918-147-victim980" type="victimName">
                        Moses 
                        Simons
                     <interp inst="t18020918-147-victim980" type="surname" value="Simons"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18020918-147-victim980" type="given" value="Moses"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18020918-147-victim980" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                        <join result="offenceVictim" targOrder="Y" targets="t18020918-147-off768 t18020918-147-victim980"></join>
                     </persName>
                  , in his dwelling-house
            </rs>.(The prisoner being a foreigner, a Jury of half foreigners were sworn.)</p>
         
